thread.title_full: American Frame americanframe.com reviewed by Emily

author: Emily
title: Emily
text: What a delightful company to work with. I had been looking for months for a good framer, having tired of spending hundreds of dollars for simple frames. American Frame popped up in Google search, and I've now framed 8 canvas paintings with their product. They have a deep selection, and once I ordered, the frames were in-hand by the end of the week. Great work!
